      "raw_text": "Stringent opposition is being\nshown by the people on the hill\nwho live near the corne. of Fifth\navenue and Adams street against\nthe building of the proposed car\nline up Fifth to the corner Of\nAdams. 'SNHH\n\n\nA petition was filed with the city\nclerk this morning which will be re-\nferred to the council 1t is signed\nby number of the prominent citi\nzens and and asks that the Wash.\nington Water Power company be\nnot granted the right to lay track\non Fifth avenue. This is the third\npaper filed in this matter."
